The \emph{converse} of the statement

\begin{align*}
\displaystyle
A \Rightarrow B
\end{align*} is

\begin{align*}
\displaystyle
B \Rightarrow A
\end{align*}

The \emph{contrapositive} of the statement

\begin{align*}
\displaystyle
A \Rightarrow B
\end{align*} is

\begin{align*}
\lnot B \Rightarrow \lnot A
\end{align*}

